title: 'Clasp breaks easily'
body: 'Overall decent but the clasp broke on the first day of use. Can now use it for storing files but can’t carry it anywhere outside because it falls open.'

title: 'Not upto the mark'
body: The item is of at most average quality..the finishing is not good..the sleeves are of poor quality...1 sleeve was already damaged..not sure if this document holder will last long on regular usage...can only be used to store documents and not for daily use..for daily use better look in local market or some better quality one's...
